title: Métro Station "La Chapelle"
description:
Métro  line 2 - on elevated section.
Connects via underground corridor with suburban section of Gare du Nord, for RER B (platform 43 to CDG Airport) and RER D.
Allow five minutes walk between métro line 2 and RER B & D.

title: Stalingrad Métro station
description: Stalingrad is a Paris Métro station at the border of the 10th arrondissement to the 19th arrondissement at the crossing of lines 2, 5 and 7, located at the Place Stalingrad which is named for the Battle of Stalingrad.
